name: City of the Tombs - 003
description: An ancient city stands - on mountains, stone and steel.  Bought and paid, the graves were laid:  millenia spanning deal.  But in each generation, they rise to kill again.  Our ties bonded in blood and earth EXCLUSIVELY ON HEN.  This series was created by artificial intelligence from about 40 or so different photographs - I chose my 8 favorite out of a whole bunch of different renderings..
